00:23:44.000 --> 00:23:46.000
nobody else knows how to do.

00:23:46.000 --> 00:23:48.000
You are the single point of failure.

00:23:48.000 --> 00:23:53.000
You stop being able to go on vacation or get sick.

00:23:53.000 --> 00:23:56.000
And I, as a contractor, as a freelancer

00:23:56.000 --> 00:23:59.000
who did Shiny Freelance, I saw this happen a lot

00:23:59.000 --> 00:24:01.000
where people were looking for a contractor

00:24:01.000 --> 00:24:02.000
to come pick up the pieces of something

00:24:02.000 --> 00:24:04.000
that someone had left unexpectedly

00:24:04.000 --> 00:24:06.000
that no one could run.

00:24:06.000 --> 00:24:08.000
And it might be running on ShinyApps.io,

00:24:08.000 --> 00:24:11.000
but nobody knew how to update it

00:24:11.000 --> 00:24:14.000
or they couldn't run it locally and it would break.

00:24:14.000 --> 00:24:17.000
Yeah, I think that that's a big pain point

00:24:17.000 --> 00:24:18.000
that people don't think about

00:24:18.000 --> 00:24:20.000
until they're in the situation.

