when I do make changes to that repo,

00:27:04.000 --> 00:27:07.000
it will automatically update on Connect Cloud.

00:27:07.000 --> 00:27:10.000
And a big update from ShinyApps.io

00:27:10.000 --> 00:27:13.000
is this idea of putting in secret variables

00:27:13.000 --> 00:27:15.000
at the time of deployment.

00:27:15.000 --> 00:27:18.000
So for those that have done anything in ShinyApps.io

00:27:18.000 --> 00:27:22.000
with database credentials, username or password,

00:27:22.000 --> 00:27:24.000
or LLM keys, right,

00:27:24.000 --> 00:27:27.000
you're putting them probably like in some kind of RN file,

00:27:27.000 --> 00:27:28.000
like within your project,

00:27:28.000 --> 00:27:30.000
and just putting it up into the cloud,

00:27:30.000 --> 00:27:33.000
which is still, you know, it's still there in the bundle, right,

00:27:33.000 --> 00:27:36.000
which is not a great way to keep a lot of your things,

