especially when you're going out to other systems.

00:27:38.000 --> 00:27:39.000
So what you can do here

00:27:39.000 --> 00:27:41.000
is you could put in your database credentials.

00:27:41.000 --> 00:27:44.000
Once you store them, we can never see them again.

00:27:44.000 --> 00:27:45.000
You can never see them again,

00:27:45.000 --> 00:27:48.000
but they can power your applications in a more secure way.

00:27:48.000 --> 00:27:49.000
Yes, this is amazing

