That's so much nicer than a randomly generated ID.

00:29:57.000 --> 00:30:04.000
And this is like a good place to talk about the possibility,

00:30:04.000 --> 00:30:07.000
even with a free account of Blue-Green deployment,

00:30:07.000 --> 00:30:09.000
where like you could just,

00:30:09.000 --> 00:30:12.000
if you had an extra slot in your free account, right?

00:30:12.000 --> 00:30:15.000
